{
  "stem": "21004.7",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Covered everything up, and I start going to digging a hole.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Now, I start going digging a hole but so many branches with so many trees, I had to take every tree all around, with the tree and with the mud, take and put them away 20-- I'd say 20 yard, make clear the whole place.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Later dig out the mud.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The bunker was like 30-- 30 by 20 feet long.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Then start going, and I dig all of this out, all the mud.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I went and start going in different sections far away, cutting trees, round trees like this, maybe a little heavier, cut them, schlep them, bringing over here.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And you start building like this, throwing around, throw this way and one wall, the other wall, all around build up those trees, and the bunker all around.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Later I made for my wife a place where to cook.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So we had barley, we have all kind of other food, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You cooking soup in a big pot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So I cut two big tree-- you know, two trees.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They were so heavy, so heavy, putting over here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Dig a hole and to make a fire with wood, make a fire, and put the pot on top.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And then she was cooking with water.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Brought water from a lake far away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Went for water, brought water.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And she was cooking here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And my wife and my cousin was sitting here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I say watch.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "If it start burning down already, those pieces of wood, you got two other pieces, and I got two more on the both sides to push it in.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But it wouldn't burn through.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "It fell.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "So I gave them the order, and I went there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Then I hear a scream, screaming terrible.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
